[TITLE]
Parallel pumps — two pumps on same junction pair share flow

[JUNCTIONS]
J1    0    500

[RESERVOIRS]
R1    0

[PUMPS]
PMP1    R1    J1    HEAD C1
PMP2    R1    J1    HEAD C2

[CURVES]
;PUMP: Head curve for pump 1 (larger capacity)
C1    0    400
C1    500    300
C1    1000    100
;PUMP: Head curve for pump 2 (smaller capacity)
C2    0    400
C2    300    300
C2    600    100

[ENERGY]
Global Efficiency    75

[OPTIONS]
Units    GPM
Headloss    H-W

[TIMES]
Duration    6:00
Hydraulic Timestep    1:00
Report Timestep    1:00

[END]
